  breadcrumbs={[{ label: 'Home', href: '/' }, { label: 'About' }]}
>
  <h1>About Trilogy</h1>
  <img src="/files/trilogyincar-unit-lrg.jpg" class="highlight_image_big" alt="Trilogy workshop" />
  <p>Trilogy was formed in 1997 and at this time could offer mobile installation of all vehicle electronic devices, after a couple of years we moved into a workshop in Ashton under Lyne as we were doing more and more complicated and large installations which we could simply not do out on site.</p>
  <div class="text-with-image">
    <div>
      <p>After the success of this move and the requirement for even more space we decided to move to Stalybridge in 2003 and have been here ever since.</p>
      <p>At our workshop we can undertake the installation of most vehicle electrical or electronic devices being authorised dealers for the leading manufacturers we can custom design a security system or Tracking device to add to your vehicle no matter what type of vehicle you own, we can easily cater for all cars &amp; vans, motorcycles, motorhomes &amp; caravans and plant machinery. We can also cater for all your fleet management requirements by supplying and fitting fleet tracking systems from award winning manufacturer Smarttrack.</p>
    </div>
    <img src="/files/repair-of-vehicle-electrical-and-electronic-systems.gif" class="highlight_image" alt="Car audio &amp; alarm installation" />
  </div>
  <div class="text-with-image">
    <div>
      <p>We can supply, fit and repair hands free systems into your vehicle and we are Certified installers for Parrot hands free systems and can offer spares, repairs and software updates. With our experience we can fully integrate these systems into your vehicle which can allow you to get the best performance from your system.</p>
      <p>We can supply and fit any hifi or multimedia system to your exact requirements. From a CD player fitting, an ipod integration kit or a full multimedia system with navigation, DVD, roof or headrest monitors we are capable of all these types of installations. If you have your own equipment we are happy to install it or repair it.</p>
    </div>
    <img src="/files/trilogy-sign.jpg" class="highlight_image" alt="Trilogy Stalybridge" />
  </div>
  <div class="text-with-image">
    <div>
      <p>Struggle parking? We offer a range of solutions from front and rear parking sensors to reversing cameras all integrated into your vehicle.</p>
      <p>We can undertake electrical repair work on your vehicle systems such as electric windows, central locking, heaters or lights and can supply electric window and central locking conversion kits.</p>
    </div>
    <img src="/files/parrot-teach-your-car-to-talk-here.jpg" class="highlight_image" alt="Parrot hands free" />
  </div>
  <p>To list everything we can do would fill the page but with over 25 years experience in fitting vehicle electronics there is nothing we haven't seen or been asked for at some time or another, even if you have your own equipment no matter what it is, just give us a call and see if we can install it for you.</p>
  <hr />
